{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895099188,"sessionID":"ses_284678099ffeSiKrtSZ4Z4XGwT","part":{"id":"prt_d7b98b58b001PvzjqN4D33EiVT","messageID":"msg_d7b9892ee001usSG3EbZC3mkiy","sessionID":"ses_284678099ffeSiKrtSZ4Z4XGwT","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-ae1d96b71ba34c6ebd734f53b1ec6ec1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-037/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-037/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-037 — PCAP 分析器示例应用 Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-037 — PCAP 分析器示例应用 |\n8: | Module | example |\n9: | Language | Python |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Task Checklist\n16: \n17: ### Phase 1: Directory Structure (ST-1)\n18: \n19: - [ ] **T1.1**: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/` directory\n20:   - Purpose: PCAP analyzer example root\n21:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/`\n22:   - Verification: `test -d example/pcap-analyzer`\n23: \n24: - [ ] **T1.2**: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/parsers/` directory\n25:   - Purpose: Protocol parser modules location\n26:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/parsers/`\n27:   - Verification: `test -d example/pcap-analyzer/parsers`\n28: \n29: - [ ] **T1.3**: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/utils/` directory\n30:   - Purpose: Utility modules location\n31:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/utils/`\n32:   - Verification: `test -d example/pcap-analyzer/utils`\n33: \n34: - [ ] **T1.4**: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/tests/` directory\n35:   - Purpose: Unit tests location\n36:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/tests/`\n37:   - Verification: `test -d example/pcap-analyzer/tests`\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T1.5**: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/sample_data/` directory\n40:   - Purpose: Sample test data location\n41:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/sample_data/`\n42:   - Verification: `test -d example/pcap-analyzer/sample_data`\n43: \n44: ### Phase 2: Configuration Constants (ST-2)\n45: \n46: - [ ] **T2.1**: Define `SERVER_HOST` constant in `pcap_analyzer.py`\n47:   - Purpose: HTTP bind address\n48:   - Value: `\"0.0.0.0\"`\n49:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n50:   - Verification: `grep \"SERVER_HOST\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n51: \n52: - [ ] **T2.2**: Define `SERVER_PORT` constant in `pcap_analyzer.py`\n53:   - Purpose: HTTP listen port\n54:   - Value: `8000`\n55:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n56:   - Verification: `grep \"SERVER_PORT\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n57: \n58: - [ ] **T2.3**: Define `SERVER_RELOAD` constant in `pcap_analyzer.py`\n59:   - Purpose: Development auto-reload flag\n60:   - Value: `True`\n61:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n62:   - Verification: `grep \"SERVER_RELOAD\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n63: \n64: - [ ] **T2.4**: Define `DEFAULT_API_BASE` constant in `pcap_analyzer.py`\n65:   - Purpose: OpenAI-compatible API base URL\n66:   - Value: `\"https://api.siliconflow.cn/v1\"`\n67:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n68:   - Verification: `grep \"DEFAULT_API_BASE\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n69: \n70: - [ ] **T2.5**: Define `DEFAULT_MODEL` constant in `pcap_analyzer.py`\n71:   - Purpose: Default LLM model name\n72:   - Value: `\"Qwen/QwQ-32B\"`\n73:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n74:   - Verification: `grep \"DEFAULT_MODEL\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n75: \n76: - [ ] **T2.6**: Define `DEFAULT_INTERPRETER_NAME` constant in `pcap_analyzer.py`\n77:   - Purpose: Sandbox interpreter name\n78:   - Value: `\"my-interpreter\"`\n79:   - File: `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n80:   - Verification: `grep \"DEFAULT_INTERPRETER_NAME\" example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n81: