 Verification: `grep \"informer-path\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T1.5**: Add lister-path parameter for listers output\n40:   - Purpose: Generate listers in client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/\n41:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n42:   - Verification: `grep \"lister-path\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T1.6**: Add --with-watch flag to generate watch-capable clients\n45:   - Purpose: Enable Watch method in typed clients\n46:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n47:   - Verification: `grep \"with-watch\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n48: \n49: - [ ] **T1.7**: Add API group version specification runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n50:   - Purpose: Specify correct API group for generation\n51:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n52:   - Verification: `grep \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\" hack/update-codegen.sh || grep \"runtime/v1alpha1\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T1.8**: Add output-pkg parameter for module path\n55:   - Purpose: Set correct module import path github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go\n56:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n57:   - Verification: `grep \"output-pkg=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n58: \n59: ### Phase 2: Boilerplate Header File (ST-2)\n60: \n61: - [ ] **T2.1**: Create hack/boilerplate.go.txt header file\n62:   - Purpose: Provide copyright header template for generated code\n63:   - File: `hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n64:   - Verification: `test -f hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n65: \n66: - [ ] **T2.2**: Add copyright year placeholder in boilerplate\n67:   - Purpose: Use dynamic year for copyright headers\n68:   - File: `hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n69:   - Verification: `grep \"YEAR\" hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n70: \n71: - [ ] **T2.3**: Add Apache 2.0 license header in boilerplate\n72:   - Purpose: Include license information in generated code\n73:   - File: `hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n74:   - Verification: `grep \"Apache License\" hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n75: \n76: ### Phase 3: Client-go Directory Structure (ST-3)\n77: \n78: - [ ] **T3.1**: Create client-go/ directory\n79:   - Purpose: Initialize client-go module directory\n80:   - File: `client-go/`\n81:   - Verification: `test -d client-go`\n82: \n83: - [ ] **T3.2**: Create client-go/go.mod with module path\n84:   - Purpose: Define Go module for client-go package\n85:   - File: `client-go/go.mod`\n86:   - Verification: `grep \"module github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go\" client-go/go.mod`\n87: \n88: - [ ] **T3.3**: Add k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1 dependency to go.mod\n89:   - Purpose: Include Kubernetes client library dependency\n90:   - File: `client-go/go.mod`\n91:   - Verification: `grep \"k8s.io/client-go\" client-go/go.mod`\n92: \n93: - [ ] **T3.4**: Add k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1 dependency to go.mod\n94:   - Purpose: Include API machinery types dependency\n95:   - File: `client-go/go.mod`\n96:   - Verification: `grep \"k8s.io/apimachinery\" client-go/go.mod`\n97: \n98: - [ ] **T3.5**: Create client-go/clientset/ directory\n99:   - Purpose: Initialize clientset subdirectory\n100:   - File: `client-go/clientset/`\n101:   - Verification: `test -d client-go/clientset`\n102: \n103: - [ ] **T3.6**: Create client-go/informers/ directory\n104:   - Purpose: Initialize informers subdirectory\n105:   - File: `client-go/informers/`\n106:   - Verification: `test -d client-go/informers`\n107: \n108: - [ ] **T3.7**: Create client-go/listers/ directory\n109:   - Purpose: Initialize listers subdirectory\n110:   - File: `client-go/listers/`\n111:   - Verification: `test -d client-go/listers`\n112: \n113: ### Phase 4: Generate Clientset Code (ST-4)\n114: \n115: - [ ] **T4.1**: Run make gen-client to generate clientset\n116:   - Purpose: Execute code generation for clientset\n117:   - File: `Makefile`\n118:   - Verification: `make gen-client`\n119: \n120: - [ ] **T4.2**: Verify client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go exists\n121:   - Purpose: Confirm Clientset struct and Interface generated\n122:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n123:   - Verification: `test -f client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n124: \n125: - [ ] **T4.3**: Verify Clientset Interface has Discovery method\n126:   - Purpose: Confirm discovery client integration\n127:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n128:   - Verification: `grep \"Discovery()\" client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n129: \n130: - [ ] **T4.4**: Verify Clientset Interface has RuntimeV1alpha1 method\n131:   - Purpose: Confirm runtime group accessor generated\n132:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n133:   - Verification: `grep \"RuntimeV1alpha1()\" client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n134: \n135: - [ ] **T4.5**: Verify NewForConfig constructor exists\n136:   - Purpose: Confirm main constructor generated\n137:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n138:   - Verification: `grep \"NewForConfig\" client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n139: \n140: - [ ] **T4.6**: Verify NewForConfigOrDie constructor exists\n141:   - Purpose: Confirm panic-on-error constructor generated\n142:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n143:   - Verification: `grep \"NewForConfigOrDie\" client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`\n144: \n145: - [ ] **T4.7**: Verify scheme/register.go exists\n146:   - Purpose: Confirm Scheme and Codecs generated\n147:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n148:   - Verification: `test -f client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n149: \n150: - [ ] **T4.8**: Verify Scheme variable is exported\n151:   - Purpose: Confirm Scheme for type registration\n152:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n153:   - Verification: `grep \"var Scheme\" client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n154: \n155: - [ ] **T4.9**: Verify Codecs variable is exported\n156:   - Purpose: Confirm Codecs for serialization\n157:   - File: `client-go/clients